verbose_text: Regarding the effect of autophagy on cell viability, it was observed that the viability in the H 2 O 2 group was decreased compared with that in the control group, whereas rapamycin increased cell viability and 3-MA decreased cell viability compared with that in the H 2 O 2 group (XREF_FIG).
evidence: rapamycin increased cell viability and 3-MA decreased cell viability
